name: Play to save the dinosaurs
description: @sianvictoriauk - self portrait - Part 1: I’ve entered a dimension where high energy lasers are being used to eliminate the dinosaur race. I must find a way to prevent the extinction of these unique creatures from technology and climate change while collecting bitcoins along the way to upgrade my defence.  Do I lure the dinosaur away from the volcanic eruption? Or do I quickly collect the bitcoins I can find on my way to the top of the mountain to have enough defence to take out the high energy lasers?  The fate of the dinosaur race is in your hands. What happens next?
